==English==

===Etymology===
*[[pseudo-]] + [[science]]

===Noun===
'''pseudoscience'''
# '''1844''' Any body of [[knowledge]] purported to be scientific or supported by [[science]] but which fails to comply with the [[scientific method]].

===Usage note===
This term may be used by people who have no underlying familiarity with the subject under consideration, and thus may be seen as pejorative.  Its use should be avoided in the absence of relevant information.

